# AI 流式对话: Java 网关 → Python 微服务 端到端测试
#
# 链路: 浏览器 → Java :8000 /api/ai/chat-stream → 转发 Python :8001 /chat/stream
# Java 注入 X-User-Id header (从 JWT 拿 user_id), Python 用它构造 thread_id

############################################
#  Step 1: 登录拿 JWT
############################################

### 1. 登录 (tester/123456)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username": "tester", "password": "123456"}

> {%
client.global.set("token", response.body.data);
%}

############################################
#  Step 2: 流式聊天 — 关键测试
############################################

### 2. 基础对话 (没工具, 没 RAG)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "你好, 介绍一下自己",
  "conversation_id": "java-flow-1"
}


### 3. 调时间工具 (验证工具循环转发)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "现在几点了?",
  "conversation_id": "java-flow-2"
}


### 4. 开知识库, 问鸣潮角色 (验证 RAG 转发)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "绯雪是什么属性?",
  "conversation_id": "java-flow-3",
  "enable_knowledge": true
}


### 5. 开联网搜索 (验证开关透传)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "今天有什么科技新闻?",
  "conversation_id": "java-flow-4",
  "enable_search": true
}


### 6. 多轮对话 (验证 user_id 隔离, 记忆生效)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "我叫张三, 记住",
  "conversation_id": "java-flow-5"
}

### 6.2 接上 — 用同 conversation_id 问名字
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "我叫什么名字?",
  "conversation_id": "java-flow-5"
}


############################################
#  Step 3: 安全测试 — 无 token / 假 token
############################################

### 7. 无 token (应该 401)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/chat-stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{"message": "你好", "conversation_id": "no-token"}


### 8. 假 token (应该 401)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer fake.token.here
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{"message": "你好", "conversation_id": "fake-token"}


### 问 "我有哪些角色"
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"message": "我有哪些角色?", "conversation_id": "resonator-test"}